134
00:12:18,860 --> 00:12:20,260
My drawings.

135
00:12:41,740 --> 00:12:43,050
Are you from the ancient times?

136
00:12:43,260 --> 00:12:44,780
Should I make you a small river

137
00:12:44,780 --> 00:12:46,740
