263
00:20:27,940 --> 00:20:28,740
I've always wanted to

264
00:20:28,740 --> 00:20:30,140
fit in with you.

265
00:20:31,420 --> 00:20:33,220
But since I was little,

266
00:20:33,980 --> 00:20:35,700
