No.

272
00:20:41,900 --> 00:20:43,500
You think too much.

273
00:20:43,300 --> 00:20:49,140
♫The weather changed suddenly, and my world changed♫

274
00:20:46,020 --> 00:20:46,940
After all,

275
00:20:47,700 --> 00:20:49,010
there are things

276
00:20:50,180 --> 00:20:51,180
